A vintage-style illustration of an elegant Victorian-era butler with an elaborate curled mustache, carefully arranging delicate paper documents on an ornate wooden desk. The butler wears white gloves and a formal tailcoat. Each document appears to transform into origami-like shapes as he handles them. The scene is lit by warm candlelight casting golden hues across rich mahogany wood and brass fixtures. Sepia and amber tones dominate, with intricate cross-hatching and fine linework reminiscent of 19th-century engravings. The documents flow and swirl in an organized dance around his hands, suggesting transformation and templating magic.
